CLI tools for repository management

Usage: rhino-cli [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  test-coverage    Test coverage commands
  spec-coverage    BDD spec coverage commands
  docs             Documentation validation commands
  agents           Agent configuration commands
  repo-governance  Repository governance validation commands
  workflows        Workflow definition commands
  git              Git workflow commands
  contracts        Contract codegen post-processing commands
  java             Java validation commands
  env              Environment file backup and restore commands
  doctor           Check required tool versions are installed and correct
  help             Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -v, --verbose          verbose output with timestamps
  -q, --quiet            quiet mode (errors only)
  -o, --output <OUTPUT>  output format: text, json, markdown [default: text]
      --no-color         disable colored output
      --say <SAY>        echo a message to stdout [default: ""]
  -h, --help             Print help
  -V, --version          Print version

